      Form
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Apply for a keeper's certificate for a trailer
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Apply to get a 'certificate of keeper' for a trailer if you're its registered keeper, or get a replacement if the original is lost, stolen or destroyed.


  </p>

  </div>
</div>

