<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Use this form to apply for a keeper’s certificate for a trailer, or to get a replacement if the original has been lost, stolen or destroyed.</p>

<p>You need to keep the certificate in your vehicle if you take the trailer abroad.</p>

<div role="note" aria-label="Information" class="application-notice info-notice">
<p>You also need to separately <a href="https://www.gov.uk/register-trailer-to-take-abroad">register your trailer with DVLA if you want to take it abroad</a>.</p>
</div>

<h2 id="send-the-form-online">Send the form online</h2>

<ol class="steps">
<li>
<p>Download and fill in the application form.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Save the application form on your computer.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Send the application form to the Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (<abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency">DVSA</abbr>) using the service to <a href="https://www.gov.uk/apply-vehicle-test-certificate-lorry-trailer">apply for a certificate for a trailer</a>. You also need to send supporting documents.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Pay the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/heavy-goods-vehicle-fees/heavy-goods-vehicle-hgv-and-trailer-test-fees#certificate-of-keeper">application fee</a> by credit or debit card (<abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency">DVSA</abbr> will tell you how to do this after you’ve applied), or by cheque or using a <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/vosa-pre-funded-customer-account-application-form">pre-funded account</a>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p>The supporting documents you need to send are copies of:</p>

<ul>
  <li>the vehicle’s registration documents</li>
  <li>the manufacturer’s build specifications</li>
  <li>the ministry plating certificate</li>
  <li>any other relevant information</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="send-the-form-by-post">Send the form by post</h2>

<p>You can also send the application and supporting documents by post.</p>

<div class="address"><div class="adr org fn"><p>

Technical and Support Services 
<br></br><abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency">DVSA</abbr> 
<br></br>The Ellipse 
<br></br>Padley Road 
<br></br>Swansea 
<br></br>SA1 8AN 
<br></br>
</p></div></div>

<div role="note" aria-label="Information" class="application-notice info-notice">
<p>Your application can be delayed if you do not fill in the application form correctly.</p>
</div>

</div>
</div>

